ped to match the depth		      image. 		     		     		      raw_depth_$ID.png : this is a 16-bit png image		      containing the depth values (depth measured in		      millimeters). The raw depth is not processed or		      cropped in any way.		      		     		     		      depth_$ID.exr : this is a floating point		      image containing the depth values (depth		      measured in centimeters)		     		     		      depth_$ID.png : this is a 16-bit png 		      image containing the depth values (depth		      measured in millimeters)		     		    	       	       	      		  		    Camera Intrinsics  		 		   		 		      		       Intel/Creative 		       ASUS/Xtion 		       Depth Camera - Horizontal Field of View 		       74 deg 		       58.590660 		       Depth Camera - Vertical Field of View 		       58 deg 		       45.642715 		       Color Camera - Horizontal Field of View 		       65 deg 		       58.590660 		       Color Camera - Vertical Field of View 		       54 deg 		       45.642715 		       Depth Resolution - Horizontal 		       320 		       320 		       Depth Resolution - Vertical 		       240 		       240 		       Color Resolution - Horizontal 		       640 		       640 		       Color Resolution - Vertical 		       480 		       480 		       Depth Focal Length 		       224.502 		         525.0   		       Color Focal Length 		       583.079 		         525.0    		       	       	       		 		    			      Test Sequences  		   		   		  		     		      		       			 HCI_FAR0 ASUS/Xtion (Download Here) 			      		      		      		      		       			 HCI_FAR1 ASUS/Xtion (Download Here) 			      		      		      		      		       			 HCI_FAR2 ASUS/Xtion (Download Here) 			      		      		      		      		       			 HCI_FAR3 ASUS/Xtion (Download Here) 			      		      		      		      		       			 HCI_FAR4 ASUS/Xtion (Download Here) 			      		      		      		      		       			 HCI_FAR5 ASUS/Xtion (Download Here) 			      		      		      		      		       			 HCI_FAR6 ASUS/Xtion (Download He